title: Whirlpool Top-Freezer Refrigerator - WRT104TFDW
description:
Whirlpool White Top-Freezer Refrigerator - WRT104TFDW

Fit all of your fresh and frozen favorites without sacrificing any space with the 28" wide top-freezer refrigerator with 14 cu. ft. capacity. Enjoy quiet cooling with improved design and ice cold temperatures inside the top-freezer refrigerator with freezer temperature controls, and you'll always have plenty of ice on hand with the optional icemaker.
